Add $10+80$ then add $4$ then add $3$.

$\begin{align}
\blueE{14}+\purpleD{83}&=\blueE{10}+\blueE{4}+\purpleD{80}+\purpleD3\\\\
&= \blueE{10}+\purpleD{80}+\blueE{4}+\purpleD{3}
\end{align}$

**Yes**, this strategy works.

Add $14+80$ then add $3$.

